casebody.data:
MORSE et al., Appellants, v. FREOIT, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Tracy H. Morse and others against Charles J. Freoit.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment of the county court reversed, with costs, and the judgment of the justice’s court affirmed, with costs.
